    DefineShape3Tag

    public class DefineShape2Tag
extends DefineShapeTag
    Represents a DefineShape2 tag in a SWF file.

    DefineShape2 extends the capabilities of DefineShapeTag with the ability to support more than 255 styles in the style list and multiple style lists in a single shape.
